window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>\"When we entered the caves, I didn't know what to expect. But the further we delved, the more questions I had.\"</b></p> <p>When Asher Merrick was reincarnated to the world of Echo Veil, he was given tremendous power to unlock his potential for short bursts of amazing feats. That all comes crashing down after a chance encounter with the Nightstrike clan, Giezha's former goliath tribe.</p> <p>After a precocious investor whisks them away to the sleepy fishing town of Bouldergulf, they prepare to enter the mountains, hoping to find treasure beyond compare. But when Asher tries to save someone from the brutal power struggle unfolding in the Nighstrike Clan, everyone learns that there's more than just treasure hidden away inside the mountains.</p> <p>Will Asher reconnect to his power after a debilitating injury? Can Giezha save her brother from the mighty Zha'lin? And will the Red Breaker guild make it out of the caves?</p> <p><i>Reborn a Warrior</i> is the scintillating, exciting, and action-packed sequel to <i>Reborn a Hero</i>. Filled with thrilling magic, exciting locations, and unconventional relationships featuring the lovely adventuring quartet of Mara Brightwood, Uli Siannodel, Giezha Nightstrike, and Kiersa Denrel, <i>Reborn a Warrior</i> is the spicy isekai fantasy you've been looking for.</p>"; 
